---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components'

import { createContactURL } from '@/coruz.net.config'
---

<section id="support" class="bg-accent w-full py-12" aria-labelledby="support-heading">
  <div class="main-container flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-10 lg:flex-row">
    <div
      class="group flex flex-col items-center gap-6 text-center md:flex-row md:items-start md:text-left"
    >
      <div
        class="shrink-0 rounded-2xl bg-white/20 p-4 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110"
      >
        <Icon
          name="fa6-solid:user-gear"
          class="h-8 w-8 transform-[translateZ(0)] text-white will-change-transform backface-hidden md:h-10 md:w-10"
          aria-hidden="true"
        />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2
          id="support-heading"
          class="mb-2 text-lg font-black tracking-wider text-white uppercase sm:text-2xl"
        >
          ¿Ya eres cliente y necesitas ayuda?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-light-primary max-w-xl text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium sm:text-base">
          Nuestro equipo de soporte está listo para asistirte de inmediato con cualquier detalle
          técnico o duda sobre tu sitio.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <a
      class="text-accent font-display bg-white px-12 py-5 text-center text-sm font-bold uppercase shadow-xl shadow-black/10 transition-all duration-300 outline-none hover:bg-white/90 focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-white focus-visible:ring-offset-2 sm:text-base"
      href={createContactURL('e-problem')}
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      aria-label="Reportar un problema (abre el cliente de correo)"
    >
      Reportar Problema
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
